Safaricom opens regional hub for Eastern Kenya. Safaricom has opened its 45th shop in Kitengela town and unveiled its Nairobi East Regional Office as part of its ongoing strategy to increase customer touch points. The Nairobi East Regional Office, situated at the Sameer Business Park will act as a hub for the wider Machakos, Kitui and Makueni counties as well as the nearby Kajiado county and neighbouring parts of Nairobi. The Kitengela shop will become the eighth standalone shop located in the region.